apple_vendor_description: This depiction of a couple on Apple devices showcases two women with medium-light to light skin tones, sharing a moment of deep affection. The iconic red heart between them pulsates with glossy 3D shading, its smooth gradients and realistic lighting conveying genuine warmth. Apple’s signature soft rounded edges give the figures a friendly and approachable appearance, perfect for expressing love, partnership, and strong bonds.
